Subprog SETBRWX3()    # Mettre à jour la clé composite pour les browsers X3
Local Integer WI

WI=0: Gosub AYD
Close Local File [AY1],[AY2]
End

WI=0: Gosub AYF
Close Local File [AY1],[AY2]
WI=0: Gosub AYA
Close Local File [AY1],[AY2]
WI=0: Gosub AYB
Close Local File [AY1],[AY2]
